**Phase 5.4 complete.** Here's what was implemented:

**SwipeableProductCard** (`components/product/swipeable-product-card.tsx`):
- Swipe left on any product card reveals a wishlist toggle action panel (72px) with heart icon and haptic feedback
- Long-press (500ms) shows a centered quick preview modal with title, brand, family/concentration badges, price, description, longevity/sillage labels, wishlist toggle, and "View Details" link
- Click prevention during swipe avoids accidental navigation
- Desktop: invisible wrapper via `md:contents` — cards render as direct grid children unchanged

**PullToRefresh** (`components/ui/pull-to-refresh.tsx`):
- Touch pull-down from top of page with resistance factor, spinner indicator, 80px threshold triggers `router.refresh()` for ISR revalidation
- Mobile-only (`md:hidden`)

**Integration**: Both components integrated on all 4 catalog pages — `/products`, `/search`, `/collections/[slug]`, `/moods/[slug]`.

